            "code": true,
            "reference": {
              "kind": "source",
              "path": "packages/canvas/src/state/z-order.ts"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": ". Every section paints before every non-section. Among sections, containment depth sorts ascending, then area sorts descending so bigger same-depth sections sink behind smaller ones, then the original schema index is the stable final tie-breaker. Non-sections keep schema order. The CSS tiers are: section bodies at z 0, connector SVG at z 1, objects at z 2, section headers at z 3, and world overlay at z 4."
        }
      ]
